Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:25.17,main,Fitoria,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:28.88,main,Fitoria,0000,0000,0000,,You found the candidate who\N could become the next queen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:35.72,italics,Fitoria,0000,0000,0000,,She's close by, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:39.97,italics,Fitoria,0000,0000,0000,,I must go see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:01:01.33,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,1)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.61,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Release Van-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.44,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,1)}Filolial Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:23.16,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:28.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This place is done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:29.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.71,0:02:30.46,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:46.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:48.98,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:54.90,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that rotten noble released \Nthat monster just to take out Naofumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.34,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Keel-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.85,main,Ke,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:06.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, what now—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.96,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it find us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:19.39,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. We're screwed if \Nit charges at us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:21.71,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:22.89,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:23.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.52,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to fight here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:32.16,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the center of town, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:35.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I know! We'll lure it out of town first!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.31,0:03:35.89,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.27,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.28,0:03:48.49,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:49.04,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.54,0:03:51.33,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Look at Filo-chan's belly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.50,0:03:55.04,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Now look at the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.50,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's really coming after...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:03:59.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.47,0:04:00.42,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:03.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then she can lure it out of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:04.84,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.84,0:04:06.42,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.68,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take these kids and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:11.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. Please do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.19,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.68,main,Kee,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Raphtalia-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:26.78,main,Kee,0000,0000,0000,,You're in the Shield Hero's party,\N aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:27.99,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.66,0:04:31.20,main,Kee,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.75,main,Kee,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.21,0:04:38.25,main,Kee,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Keel-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:43.59,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:46.64,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go meet up with my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.80,0:04:49.05,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Van-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:54.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Keel-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.86,main,Van,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:04.36,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:06.95,main,Kee,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:08.66,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.79,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:19.28,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.55,0:05:20.91,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.81,main,G,0000,0000,0000,,Run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That way, Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.57,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:54.70,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It really is coming after Filo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:00.62,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I gave away that bracelet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.17,0:06:04.58,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's yours now. You're free to \Ndo whatever you want with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.56,0:06:19.32,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,How far are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:21.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As far as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.75,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost past the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:49.47,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,This place will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:54.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.85,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all set to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.85,0:06:58.06,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.11,0:07:05.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.79,0:07:25.84,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Zweit Aqua Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:34.43,italics,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:38.14,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's slow, but we can't even scratch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.42,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, give me some footing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.94,0:07:45.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.24,0:07:50.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Second Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:02.20,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:04.17,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,One more try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.34,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine! Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.06,0:08:27.73,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have unlimited stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:31.54,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to use the Rage Shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.45,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:37.53,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi, something seems wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.19,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:44.54,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,magic mist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:46.42,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It's a high-level magic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A magic field?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:50.13,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mean we're trapped here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:54.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I hear footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.68,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Filolials?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:13.90,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:30.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.72,sign_15645_100_Detecting_transf,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(318,1)}Detecting transformation jamming
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:39.17,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Don't resort to that power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:40.55,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.59,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:21.51,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,The Filolial Queen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.51,0:10:23.18,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,So cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:34.35,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Your body reacted badly to the Dragon \NEmperor's fragment and grew beyond control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:39.41,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If you hand over that fragment now,\N I shall spare your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.91,0:10:41.45,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But begone at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.54,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.04,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.30,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:11.15,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end this at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.13,0:11:36.75,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,The Shield Hero, I take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.63,0:11:38.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.67,0:11:42.26,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I wish to discuss many things with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.26,0:11:44.69,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,but I know this form isn't suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:46.18,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,One moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.40,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Now, to introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:09.04,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I am the queen of all \Nfilolials the world over,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.87,0:12:12.08,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Fitoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:16.38,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Fitoria?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.71,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You're her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:19.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.80,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.80,0:12:23.93,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Centuries ago, a hero of the time \Nis said to have raised a filolial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.51,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is legendary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.35,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Centuries ago"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:30.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So she inherited the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.94,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have always been Fitoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.94,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Will I also be as big as her one day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:41.65,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't feed you if you grew \N{\i1}that{\i0} big, so you'd be on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:47.57,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That would take dozens of times \Nlonger than a normal filolial's lifespan,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:49.37,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,so don't worry yourself over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.12,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she's lived that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.87,0:12:58.09,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn to introduce yourselves,\N Shield Hero's party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.09,0:12:59.96,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Iwatani Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.92,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.13,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Raphtalia. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.47,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:07.85,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.72,0:13:13.14,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,We've met before, haven't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.48,0:13:16.06,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.06,0:13:18.56,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. I'm Melty Melromarc.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.23,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pleasure to meet you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:22.11,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-tan, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.98,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Mel... tan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.28,0:13:25.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You've met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:30.33,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I ran into her on the way back to \Nthe capital after a diplomatic visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:33.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So you've made a habit of that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.95,0:13:38.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I'm grateful that \Nyou took out that monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.25,0:13:39.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you want with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:44.38,main,Mit,0000,0000,0000,,It's a long story, and this \Nisn't a great place for a chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:46.30,main,Mit,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take you somewhere more suitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.10,0:13:56.39,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like a Cardinal Hero using \Ndragon material in his equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:59.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It serves as precious fodder \Nto develop my shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:03.44,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,And I already sense an ominous \Naura in your shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:08.61,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Curse powers are certainly immense, \Nbut so are their consequences.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:09.96,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.95,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a problem. I have it under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:15.12,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Not for long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:20.42,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless, I need dragon material and \Nthe Rage Shield in order to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:24.38,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.51,0:14:31.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:36.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But the rest of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:38.69,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll order my family to bring it along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.23,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.94,0:14:42.40,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.86,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'll need you to answer several \Nquestions when we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:48.53,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Portal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:14:59.62,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Did we travel instantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Ruins, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:07.04,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You can practically feel their history.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:08.80,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,What a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.17,0:15:13.93,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I hear it's considered the remains of the \Ncivilization the original heroes defended.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.43,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You don't sound very sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:20.85,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It existed before I was born. For what \Nit's worth, I'm watching over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:24.32,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a filolial sanctuary?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:28.11,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm not supposed to bring humans here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.47,0:15:30.16,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.50,0:15:33.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess we'll be safe \Nhere for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:40.37,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.87,0:15:43.88,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a break, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:45.50,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:48.12,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,That was one long day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.88,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Keel-kun and the \Nother kids are all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.14,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They've got Van and those \Ndemi-humans with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:55.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.60,0:15:57.22,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:15:59.22,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.89,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're all hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.91,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Time to dig in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.62,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.71,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I feel too guilty to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.46,0:16:23.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.29,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it yummy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:29.76,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,They're like sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:32.46,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Right? They even eat in \Nthe same sloppy manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.39,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Naofumi-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,God, fine! I'll make you some!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.36,0:16:47.94,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me some huge pots \Nand a ton of ingredients!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.03,0:16:59.74,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd I even have to feed this KFC farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:05.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're not getting any seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:06.75,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.96,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:19.51,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how that monster \Nwas released from its seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:23.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you came to save \Nus because you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:28.73,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I was there because I was told a new \Nqueen candidate had been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:32.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A queen candidate? You mean Filo?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.86,0:17:33.99,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.40,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:36.70,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:42.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Filo growing so differently \Nthan other filolials?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:43.91,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.87,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,a hero is raising her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.30,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me. Why was the seal removed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.59,0:18:05.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:09.36,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm appalled at you Cardinal Heroes
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:12.15,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,for squabbling with the Wave nearly here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.52,0:18:14.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, they started it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.07,0:18:19.44,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I know the Shield Hero has always been \Nscorned by human supremacist countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Then you should understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:24.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're trying \Nto cross the border—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.41,0:18:25.41,top,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That won't solve a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:27.46,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Talk it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.00,0:18:30.75,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,As much as humans and demi-humans \Nmight hate each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.75,0:18:33.30,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,it is unacceptable for \Nheroes to be fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:46.48,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you Cardinal Heroes \Nknow about the hourglass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the dragon hourglass?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:51.06,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,We do know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.31,0:18:54.73,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Then why aren't you fighting \NWaves across the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:19:01.32,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying the Waves happen \Noutside of Melromarc, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:06.79,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,The Four Cardinal Heroes are meant \Nto be summoned to one country each
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.79,0:19:08.41,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,and help them fight the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:11.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,First I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.25,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going wherever I'm asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:17.55,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But you four aren't taking \Npart in any other battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.76,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, I only found out recently that other \Ncountries had their own hourglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.76,0:19:25.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I don't care about\Nwhat happens to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.68,0:19:29.73,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I fight because the hero \Nwho raised me asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,A hero asked you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:35.70,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to protect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.89,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to save the world when \Nshe doesn't care about humans?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.32,0:19:44.99,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't protect it all by myself.\N I need the heroes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But you seem far more capable than us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.16,0:19:50.71,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:52.46,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But eventually,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.94,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to save a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.80,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you need the heroes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.38,0:20:02.68,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:14.19,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the place?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.61,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:31.29,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it definitely seems like the \NThree Heroes Church is hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:35.00,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe Naofumi was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.76,0:20:45.39,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Is this an archive?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.01,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.02,0:20:57.02,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your noses out of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.77,0:21:01.11,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to make \Nup with those guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.35,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Heroes are supposed to work together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:07.66,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,That is an absolute necessity \Nin order to protect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:09.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.66,0:21:13.33,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,That country, along with those guys, \Nis trying to get rid of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.33,0:21:15.79,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard the gist of \Nwhat's been happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:18.38,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,But heroes mustn't fight among themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.66,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You seem rather obsessed with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.08,0:21:23.82,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's unacceptable, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:28.38,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,They don't wanna play nice. \NIt's a lost cause now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.29,0:21:30.70,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.41,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.78,0:21:34.88,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:36.63,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.89,0:21:43.96,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,It was all so long ago that \Nmy memory of it has faded,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:47.66,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,but I do still remember \Nthe right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.97,0:21:51.63,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,If the heroes are fighting each other
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.22,0:21:55.08,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,instead of the Waves of Catastrophe,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:01.61,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,then for the sake of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:03.94,main,Fit,0000,0000,0000,,I must kill the Four Cardinal Heroes.
